snippet.textDisplay:
Do all of the signs please!!!!
Just so you know, your sun sign is your ego, identity and “role” in life. It’s your core.
Your moon sign rules your emotions, moods and feelings. This reflects who you feel like you are inside.
Your rising or ascendent sign is your social self. Your mask. It’s what you show to people and what they see with first impressions.

I am
Sun: Gemini
Moon: Virgo
Ascending: Leo

There’s an app called co-star astrology that’s seriously amazing at breaking everything down and charting who you are! I love the app 🙌🏼
